{"tid":953513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iOS 12.1.2又爆新bug：顯示4G，但無法聯網","createTime":"2018-12-24T04:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T06:25:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3644ecba6530192f09b9579d2d562850b3576e71","tid":953513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"蘋果最新推送的iOS 12.1.2版本系統更新當中，更新日誌中有一條就是針對蜂窩移動連接的問題，蘋果稱&ldquo;解決了可能影響iPhone XR、iPhone XS 和iPhone XS Max 在土耳其的蜂窩移動連接的問題&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">除了土耳其之外，其他地區的iPhone用戶似乎變得更加糟糕</span>。多位用戶在Twitter上反饋稱自己的iPhone在升級iOS 12.1.2，即使手機的信號圖標顯示正常，但是他們卻<span style=\"color: red;\">無法使用數據網絡連接網絡。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，蘋果官方Twitter賬號下也出現了許多用戶關於數據網絡的求助信息。<br />\n<br />\n在iOS 12.1.2版本發布更新之後，數據網絡問題似乎出現在全球更多地區用戶的iPhone上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCzsQH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCzsQH7.jpg&h=625b72be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPBnEBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPBnEBs.jpg&h=5a068f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/402/113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F402%2F113.htm&d=BOTFg90aRdpsR6jSq54p9p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=59a348d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/402/113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d047dc00919092d7ffed101f5d483dd84d1c3aaa","tid":953513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"手機的信號圖標顯示正常，但是他們卻無法使用數據網絡連接網絡<br />\n手機的信號圖標顯示正常，但是他們卻無法使用數據網絡連接網絡<br />\n手機的信號圖標顯示正常，但是他們卻無法使用數據網絡連接網絡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝假9<br />\ngay cook love<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cd5e61caf333bf1f78ee1cde5b9c212b33270b","tid":953513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"一部連電話都打唔到的物體，why call phone?"},{"p